N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 ยง 606.13 - Adoption of by-laws

State Regulations

The council may adopt, amend or repeal such bylaws as it
deems advisable, consistent with this Part, governing its activities and
procedures. Notes
